Real Packing Company, Appellee, v. Reo Packing Company et al., Appellants.Gen. No. 40,804.

(Abstract of Decision.)

Heard in third division, first district, this court at October term, 1939;opinion filed May 22, 1940;rehearing denied June 14, 1940.Stanislaus E. Basinski, for appellants; Edward S. Cody and Albert E. Hallett, Jr., of counsel; Edward L. Kowalski, for appellee; Stanley S. Piotrowski, of counsel. Opinion by Justice Hebel.

"Not to be published in full.”
